While Donuts are generally not considered healthy food Dunkin Donuts creates many colorful and tasty Donuts at their numerous stores around the city. They also have muffins bagels and danishes. They have several types of coffee that you can choose from. I don't favor their coffee so much. However people seem to like it. Dunkin Donuts originated as a Belgian company. They do know how to bake Donuts and designed them four different occasions. There are two Dunkin Donuts that I know of in Bay Ridge one on 3rd Avenue and another on Fifth Avenue. They are both handicap accessible and have basic seatings for fast food comfort. I have never tried their prepared sandwiches. Overall a bargain
